Package eu.opends.analyzer

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    DataReader  
    DataUnit
    Data object containing position and speed of the car, as well as the current date.
    DataWriter
    That class is responsible for writing drive-data.
    DeviationComputer
    This class computes the deviation of a car's driven track from a given ideal line.
    DeviationQuadrangle
    This class represents a quadrangular area between two way points and two ideal points.
    DrivingTaskLogger
    This class is used for logging driving task data to a text file.
